        <p class="titan-section-label">THE SOLUTION</p>
        <h2 class="service-problem-h2">Strategic Income Planning with Multiple Safety Nets</h2>
        <div class="service-solution-content">
            <div class="service-solution-left">
                <h3>The Bucket Strategy That Works</h3>
                <p>We divide your portfolio into three time-based buckets: immediate needs (0-2 years), medium-term growth (3-10 years), and long-term wealth building (10+ years). This protects against sequence of returns risk while maintaining growth potential.</p>
                <p>Your income comes from multiple sources — Social Security, pensions, investment withdrawals, and potentially guaranteed income products. We coordinate all sources to create predictable monthly income while minimizing taxes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-solution-right">
                <h4>Income Strategy Components:</h4>
                <ul class="service-solution-list">
                    <li>Guaranteed income floor for essential expenses</li>
                    <li>Dynamic withdrawal rates based on portfolio performance</li>
                    <li>Tax-efficient withdrawal sequencing</li>
                    <li>Cash buffer for market downturns</li>
                    <li>Growth investments for inflation protection</li>
                    <li>Social Security optimization</li>
                    <li>Healthcare and long-term care planning</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
